other_tests.findings: Infrarenal abdominal aorta ectatic to 2.0 cm with mural thrombus, resulting in luminal narrowing to 1.4 x 1.0 cm. Severe stenosis in right common iliac artery with trickle flow, and complete occlusion of left common iliac artery.
Subcutaneous emphysema and foci of free intraperitoneal air likely related to recent laparoscopic cholecystectomy.
